16#ifndef RDATA_IN_1_AAAA_28_C
17#define RDATA_IN_1_AAAA_28_C
18
19#include <isc/net.h>
20
21#define RRTYPE_AAAA_ATTRIBUTES (0)
22
23static inline isc_result_t
24fromtext_in_aaaa(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
25 isc_token_t token;
26 unsigned char addr[16];
27 isc_region_t region;
28
29 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
30 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
31
32 UNUSED(type);
33 UNUSED(origin);
34 UNUSED(options);
35 UNUSED(rdclass);
36 UNUSED(callbacks);
37
38 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token, isc_tokentype_string,
39 false));
40
41 if (inet_pton(AF_INET6, DNS_AS_STR(token), addr) != 1)
42 RETTOK(DNS_R_BADAAAA);
43 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
44 if (region.length < 16)
45 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
46 memmove(region.base, addr, 16);
47 isc_buffer_add(target, 16);
48 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
49}
50
51static inline isc_result_t
52totext_in_aaaa(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
53 isc_region_t region;
54
55 UNUSED(tctx);
56
57 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
58 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
59 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 16);
60
61 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
62 return (inet_totext(AF_INET6, &region, target));
63}
64
65static inline isc_result_t
66fromwire_in_aaaa(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
67 isc_region_t sregion;
68 isc_region_t tregion;
69
70 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
71 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
72
73 UNUSED(type);
74 UNUSED(dctx);
75 UNUSED(options);
76 UNUSED(rdclass);
77
78 isc_buffer_activeregion(source, &sregion);
79 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &tregion);
80 if (sregion.length < 16)
81 return (ISC_R_UNEXPECTEDEND);
82 if (tregion.length < 16)
83 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
84
85 memmove(tregion.base, sregion.base, 16);
86 isc_buffer_forward(source, 16);
87 isc_buffer_add(target, 16);
88 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
89}
90
91static inline isc_result_t
92towire_in_aaaa(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
93 isc_region_t region;
94
95 UNUSED(cctx);
96
97 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
98 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
99 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 16);
100
101 isc_buffer_availableregion(target, &region);
102 if (region.length < rdata->length)
103 return (ISC_R_NOSPACE);
104 memmove(region.base, rdata->data, rdata->length);
105 isc_buffer_add(target, 16);
106 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
107}
108
109static inline int
110compare_in_aaaa(ARGS_COMPARE) {
111 isc_region_t r1;
112 isc_region_t r2;
113
114 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
115 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
116 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
117 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
118 REQUIRE(rdata1->length == 16);
119 REQUIRE(rdata2->length == 16);
120
121 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &r1);
122 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &r2);
123 return (isc_region_compare(&r1, &r2));
124}
125
126static inline isc_result_t
127fromstruct_in_aaaa(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
128 dns_rdata_in_aaaa_t *aaaa = source;
129
130 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
131 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
132 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
133 REQUIRE(aaaa->common.rdtype == type);
134 REQUIRE(aaaa->common.rdclass == rdclass);
135
136 UNUSED(type);
137 UNUSED(rdclass);
138
139 return (mem_tobuffer(target, aaaa->in6_addr.s6_addr, 16));
140}
141
142static inline isc_result_t
143tostruct_in_aaaa(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
144 dns_rdata_in_aaaa_t *aaaa = target;
145 isc_region_t r;
146
147 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
148 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
149 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
150 REQUIRE(rdata->length == 16);
151
152 UNUSED(mctx);
153
154 aaaa->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
155 aaaa->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
156 ISC_LINK_INIT(&aaaa->common, link);
157
158 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
159 INSIST(r.length == 16);
160 memmove(aaaa->in6_addr.s6_addr, r.base, 16);
161
162 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
163}
164
165static inline void
166freestruct_in_aaaa(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
167 dns_rdata_in_aaaa_t *aaaa = source;
168
169 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
170 REQUIRE(aaaa->common.rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
171 REQUIRE(aaaa->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
172
173 UNUSED(aaaa);
174}

176static inline isc_result_t
177additionaldata_in_aaaa(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
178 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
179 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
180
181 UNUSED(rdata);
182 UNUSED(add);
183 UNUSED(arg);
184
185 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
186}

188static inline isc_result_t
189digest_in_aaaa(ARGS_DIGEST) {
190 isc_region_t r;
191
192 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
193 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
194
195 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
196
197 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
198}

200static inline bool
201checkowner_in_aaaa(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
202 dns_name_t prefix, suffix;
203
204 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
205 REQUIRE(rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
206
207 UNUSED(type);
208 UNUSED(rdclass);
209
210 /*
211 * Handle Active Diretory gc._msdcs.<forest> name.
212 */
213 if (dns_name_countlabels(name) > 2U) {
214 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
215 dns_name_init(&suffix, NULL);
216 dns_name_split(name, dns_name_countlabels(name) - 2,
217 &prefix, &suffix);
218 if (dns_name_equal(&gc_msdcs, &prefix) &&
219 dns_name_ishostname(&suffix, false))
220 return (true);
221 }
222
223 return (dns_name_ishostname(name, wildcard));
224}
225
226static inline bool
227checknames_in_aaaa(ARGS_CHECKNAMES) {
228
229 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_aaaa);
230 REQUIRE(rdata->rdclass == dns_rdataclass_in);
231
232 UNUSED(rdata);
233 UNUSED(owner);
234 UNUSED(bad);
235
236 return (true);
237}

239static inline int
240casecompare_in_aaaa(ARGS_COMPARE) {
241 return (compare_in_aaaa(rdata1, rdata2));
242}
